               <div type="letter_message">
                  <opener>
                     <dateline>
                        <placeName>
                           <address>
                              <rs type="place" ref="#amp_place_id_29">77 St Mark's Place
                              <lb/>N.Y.C.
                              <lb/>N.Y. 1003</rs>
                           </address>
                        </placeName>
                        <date rend="#block">
                           Nov 6 th .
                        </date>
                     </dateline>
                     <salute>
                        Dear <rs type="person" ref="#amp_person_2">Stella</rs>:
                     </salute>
                  </opener>
                  <p>
                     Many thanks for <rs type="event" ref="#amp_event_id_91">your letter</rs>. <rs type="note" ana="acdh:amp-transcript__0009.xml#ana_012">Of course,
                     <lb/>selfishly, I'm rather reli<unclear><del>v</del></unclear>eved. How horrid
                     <lb/>one is !</rs>
                  </p>
                  <p>
                     The <rs type="place" ref="#amp_place_id_15">U.S.</rs> is grim.
                  </p>
                  <closer>
                     <salute>
                        love
                     </salute>
                     <signed>
                        <rs type="person" ref="#amp_person_1">Wystan</rs><unclear>.</unclear>
                     </signed>
                  </closer>
               </div>
